### Banking Transactions API - Sample Requests
### Base URL: http://localhost:3000

### ================================================
### 1. Get API Documentation (Root)
### ================================================
GET http://localhost:3000/


### ================================================
### 2. Create a Deposit Transaction
### ================================================
POST http://localhost:3000/transactions
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "toAccount": "ACC-12345",
  "amount": 1000.00,
  "currency": "USD",
  "type": "deposit"
}


### ================================================
### 3. Create a Withdrawal Transaction
### ================================================
POST http://localhost:3000/transactions
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "fromAccount": "ACC-12345",
  "amount": 150.50,
  "currency": "USD",
  "type": "withdrawal"
}


### ================================================
### 4. Create a Transfer Transaction
### ================================================
POST http://localhost:3000/transactions
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "fromAccount": "ACC-12345",
  "toAccount": "ACC-67890",
  "amount": 250.00,
  "currency": "USD",
  "type": "transfer"
}


### ================================================
### 5. Create Another Deposit (Different Account)
### ================================================
POST http://localhost:3000/transactions
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "toAccount": "ACC-67890",
  "amount": 500.00,
  "currency": "EUR",
  "type": "deposit"
}


### ================================================
### 6. Get All Transactions
### ================================================
GET http://localhost:3000/transactions


### ================================================
### 7. Get Transaction by ID
### Replace {id} with actual transaction ID from previous responses
### ================================================
GET http://localhost:3000/transactions/{id}


### ================================================
### 8. Get Account Balance for ACC-12345
### ================================================
GET http://localhost:3000/accounts/ACC-12345/balance


### ================================================
### 9. Get Account Balance for ACC-67890
### ================================================
GET http://localhost:3000/accounts/ACC-67890/balance


