### ================================================
### TRANSACTION HISTORY FILTERING (Task 3)
### ================================================

### 17. Filter by Account ID
GET http://localhost:3000/transactions?accountId=ACC-12345


### 18. Filter by Transaction Type (lowercase)
GET http://localhost:3000/transactions?type=deposit


### 19. Filter by Transaction Type (case-insensitive - uppercase)
GET http://localhost:3000/transactions?type=TRANSFER


### 20. Filter by Transaction Type (case-insensitive - mixed case)
GET http://localhost:3000/transactions?type=Withdrawal


### 21. Filter by Date Range - Date Only Format (inclusive)
GET http://localhost:3000/transactions?from=2026-01-01&to=2026-01-31


### 22. Filter by Date Range - ISO Datetime Format
GET http://localhost:3000/transactions?from=2026-01-24T00:00:00Z&to=2026-01-24T23:59:59Z


### 23. Filter by Start Date Only (open-ended)
GET http://localhost:3000/transactions?from=2026-01-24


### 24. Filter by End Date Only (open-ended)
GET http://localhost:3000/transactions?to=2026-01-25


### 25. Combine Multiple Filters: Account + Type
GET http://localhost:3000/transactions?accountId=ACC-12345&type=transfer


### 26. Combine Multiple Filters: Account + Date Range
GET http://localhost:3000/transactions?accountId=ACC-67890&from=2026-01-01&to=2026-12-31


### 27. Combine Multiple Filters: Type + Date Range
GET http://localhost:3000/transactions?type=deposit&from=2026-01-01&to=2026-01-31


### 28. Combine All Filters
GET http://localhost:3000/transactions?accountId=ACC-12345&type=withdrawal&from=2026-01-01&to=2026-12-31


